fields.name: Calloway XR 16 Driver Gents RH
fields.description: The XR 16 Driver is where forgiveness meets fast. We worked with Boeing on our most aerodynamic head shape and a redesigned Speed Step, put in more MOI and added more speed with our next generation R•MOTO face.

fields.name: Titlest Pro v1
fields.description: The new total performance Pro V1 golf ball has been developed for every player, longer distance, more consistent flight, lower long game spin, and outstanding Drop-and-Stop™ control with a very soft feel.

fields.name: Taylormade TM18 Pro 6.0 Cart Bag
fields.description: Get easy access to all your clubs with the Taylormade TM18 Pro 6.0 Cart Bag. Only weighing 2.6kg this bag has 14 way top and padded shoulder straps for carrying. This bag also features a key lock base which keeps it firmly in place while on the trolley for 18 or 36 holes.

fields.name: Spectrum Golf Glove
fields.description: This Footjoy Spectrum Golf Glove has been crafted with premium cabretta leather for a soft feel with consistent grip, whilst the contoured easy fit which utilises an high-performance microfibre along the back of the hand which works with the angled-tab closure for a consistent fit and the PowerNet mesh across the the knuckles increases comfort, improved breathability and flexibility.
